__Issue__:

__Tag__:

__Summary__:--extra-packs work well in condition of --keep-packs

__Precondition__

1. Tested Pkgs:
2. Tested Repo: https://download.tizendev.org/snapshots/trunk/common/latest
3. Tested Conf: conf_fixtures/tizendev.cfg

__Steps__

> if [ -d ~/GBS-ROOT/local/repos ];then sudo rm ~/GBS-ROOT/local/repos -rf; fi

> if [ -d ~/GBS-ROOT/local/scratch.i586.0 ];then sudo rm ~/GBS-ROOT/local/scratch.i586.0 -rf; fi

> if [ -d ./build ];then rm build -rf; fi

> mkdir build

> cd build

> ../tools/create_proj ../specs/fake.spec

> ../tools/create_proj ../specs/sw-tools.spec

> gbs -c ../conf_fixtures/tizendev.cfg build sw-tools -A i586

> test -n "`find ~/GBS-ROOT/local/repos -name "*sw-tools*.rpm"`"

#sw-tools doesn't depand on vim
> (! sudo chroot ~/GBS-ROOT/local/scratch.i586.0/ rpm -qa|grep 'vim')

> gbs -c ../conf_fixtures/tizendev.cfg build fake -A i586 --keep-packs

> test -n "`find ~/GBS-ROOT/local/repos -name "*fake*.rpm"`"

#fake doesn't depand on vim
> (! sudo chroot ~/GBS-ROOT/local/scratch.i586.0/ rpm -qa|grep 'vim')

> gbs -c ../conf_fixtures/tizendev.cfg build fake -A i586 --keep-packs --extra-packs=vim --overwrite

#so --extra-packss can work well whith --keep-packs
> sudo chroot ~/GBS-ROOT/local/scratch.i586.0/ rpm -qa|grep 'vim'
